query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(CASE WHEN dataVenda IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as nulos,
  SUM(CASE WHEN dataVenda IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as com_data,
  SUM(CASE WHEN excluido = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as nao_excluidos
FROM vendas
